=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd6e5cc9dd18fd3092c24f3e0996ccfe7fbadb0","tid":438561,"uid":9670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你以為等收錢好爽 其實煩撚過西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申試過比人撞到total左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係咁，仲要對家不斷拖，年幾都未 settle <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買全保意外後兩星期confirm total loss已經可以去落訂，再兩個星期落地，尾數保險同對家慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過嗰年個墊底就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8026aed6417211890ce08db54c805469a79e3a2b","tid":438561,"uid":4781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你以為等收錢好爽 其實煩撚過西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申試過比人撞到total左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係咁，仲要對家不斷拖，年幾都未 settle <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買全保意外後兩星期confirm total loss已經可以去落訂，再兩個星期落地，尾數保險同對家慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過嗰年個墊底就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年部車可以賣到12萬 我買左全保 但保險話計埋折舊架車只值7萬 又要比墊底 扣埋扣埋無幾多淨 仲要等對家入左罪先可以追 好似樓上咁 對家仲有得拖 追得返都要以年計<br />\n<br />\n你話頸痛乜乜乜可以賠多d 但其實你全部要有單 自己出晒錢先 最後又未必賠足<br />\n<br />\n另外又要同保險公證行差佬來回幾次 <br />\n<br />\n撞過一次 真係勞心勞力 所以話咩隊埋去等換車 我真係勸你諗真d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f648d9549eff5636efdac8ce4a43ca3b2187ddae","tid":438561,"uid":46033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:11:22.000Z","msg":"就算全保, TOTAL 左, 都要跟拆舊陪,<br />\n投保額細左故然COVER唔晒, 買大左佢